description:
AuthToken currently has an attribute named "server_manageent_url". This should be "server_management_url". I suppose the 'm' got lost along the way.

This is a pretty easy find/replace fix...but involved database migrations so I'm not sure how easy it'll actually be.
title: AuthToken server_management_url spelled incorrectly
